\v 23 Munhu anofadzwa nemhinduro yakarurama yomuromo wake; Uye shoko, rinotaurwa nenguva yakafanira, rakanaka sei!
\p
\v 24 Nzira youpenyu yowakarurama inokwira kumusoro;
\s Kuti apukunyuke paSheori pasi.
\p
\v 25 Jehovha achaparadza imba yavanozvikudza;
\s Asi muganho wechirikadzi anousimbisa.
\p
\v 26 Mano akashata anonyangadza Jehovha;
\s Asi mashoko akachena anomufadza.
\p
\v 27 Anokarira pfuma, anotambudza imba yake;
\s Asi anovenga zvipo, achararama.
\p
\v 28 Mwoyo wowakarurama
\s unombofunga chaangapindura;
\s Asi muromo wowakaipa unodurura zvakaipa.
\p
\v 29 Jehovha ari kure navakaipa;
\s Asi anonzwa munyengetero wavakarurama.
\p
\v 3 ° Meso anobwinya anofadza mwoyo; Mashoko akanaka, anobva kumwe, anokodza mapfupa.
\p
\v 31 Nzeve, inoteerera kuraira,
\s kunoisa kuupenyu,
\s Ichagara pakati pavakachenjera.
\p
\v 32 Anoramba kurairwa, anoshora mweya wake;
\s Asi anoteerera kurairwa, anowana njere.
\p
\v 33 Kutya Jehovha kunodzidzisa
\s uchenjeri;
\s Uye kuzvininipisa kunotangira kukudzwa.
\p
\v 16
\v 1 Kurangarira kwomwoyo ndo­kwomunhu; Asi mhinduro yorurimi inobva
\s kuna Jehovha.
\p
\v 2 Nzira dzose dzomunhu anoti dzakanaka pakuona kwake;
\s Asi Jehovha anoyera zvinangwa.
\p
\v 3 Isa mabasa ako ose kuna Jehovha, Zvawakarangarira zvigoitika.
\p
\v 4 Jehovha akaitira chinhu chimwe
\s tteUttukwe bua w,ctw*,
\s Zvirokwazvo kunyange nowakaipa akaitirwa zuva rezvakashata.
\p
\v 5 Mumwe nomumwe, anomwoyo unozvikudza,
\s anonyangadza Jehovha;
\s Zvirokwazvo, haangakoni kurohwa.
\p
\v 6 Zvakaipa zvinodzikinurwa nenyasha nezvokwadi; Nokutya Jehovha vanhu vanobva
\s pane zvakashata.
\p
\v 7 Kana nzira dzomunhu dzichifadza Jehovha,
\s Anomuyananisira kunyange namapfumo ake.
\s Zviri nani kuva nezvishoma nokururama,
\s Pakuva nepfuma zhinji nokusarurama.
\p
\v 9 Mwoyo womunhu anozvifungira nzira yake;
\s Asi Jehovha anorairira kufamba kwake.
\s io Miromo yamambo inotema zvirevo zvazvokwadi;
\s Muromo wake haungaposhi pakutonga.
\s Chiyero nechienzaniso,
\s chisinganyengeri,
\s chinobva kuna Jehovha;
\s Zviidzo zvose zvehombodo ibasa
\s rake.
\p
\v 12 Zvinonyangadza kana madzimambo
\s achiita zvakaipa;
\s Nokuti chigaro choushe chinosimbiswa nokururama.
\p
\v 13 Madzimambo anofadzwa nemiromo yakarurama;
\s Anotaura zvinhu zvakarurama anodikanwa naye.
\p
\v 14 Kutsamwa kwamambo kwakaita senhume dzorufu;
\s Asi munhu akachenjera anokunyaradza.
\p
\v 15 Upenyu huri pakubwinya kwechiso chamambo;
\s Kana achifara munhu zvakaita segore
\s remvura yokupedzisira.
\p
\v 16 Kuwana uchenjeri kunokunda sei
\s kuwana ndarama;
\s zviri nani kutsaura kuwana njere pakuwana sirivha.
\p
\v 17 Mugwagwa, wakapfumba, wavakarurama
\s ndiko kubva pane zvakaipa;
\s M\Ochnjex era	yake
\s anochengeta mweya wake.
\p
\v 18 Kuzvikudza kunotangira kuparadzwa;
\s Uye mweya wamanyawi unotangira kuwa.
\s Vana vowakadai vachava noutiziro.
\p
\v 27 Kutya Jehovha itsime roupenyu; Kuti munhu apukunyuke
\s pamisungo yorufu.
\p
\v 28 Ukuru hwamambo hunoonekwa pakuwanda kwavanhu;
\s Asi kuparadzwa kwashe kuri pakushaiwa vanhu.
\p
\v 29 Ano mwoyo murefu ane njere kwazvo;
\s Asi anokurumidza kutsamwa anowedzera upenzi.
\p
\v 3 ° Mwoyo wakagadzikana ndihwo upenyu hwomuviri;
\s Asi godo rinoodza mapfupa.
\p
\v 31 Anomanikidza murombo, anozvidza Muiti wake;
\s Asi ane tsitsi nomushaiwi, anomukudza.
\p
\v 32 Akaipa anowiswa pasi mukutadza kwake;
\s Asi akarurama ane tariro pakufa kwake.
\p
\v 33 Uchenjeri hunogara pamwoyo weane njere;
\s Asi zviri mukati mamapenzi zvinozikanwa.
\p
\v 34 Kururama kunokurisa rudzi;
\s Asi zvivi zvinonyadzisa kurudzi rupi norupi.
\p
\v 35 Mambo anofarira muranda, anoita nokuchenjera;
\s Asi anonyadzisa achatsamwirwa naye.
